Importation des données

library(tidyverse)
data <- read.csv("../data_etudiant/data_1/mrna.csv", header = T, row.names = 1)
info <- read.csv("../data_etudiant/data_1/sample_group.csv", header = T, row.names = 1)

Analyses préliminaires

boxplot(data, col = as.factor(info$Y), main = "boxplot mRNA")

boxplot(t(data), col = as.factor(info$Y), main = "boxplot sample")

Filtrer les gènes peu variant

data <- data[,colSums(data) > 10]
coef.var <- function(x){
    c.var = sd(x)/mean(x)
}
coef.mRNA <- as.numeric(lapply(data, coef.var))
hist(coef.mRNA)

data.filtered <- data[,abs(coef.mRNA) > 0.2]

Transformer les données

data.logged <- log(data.filtered)
data.scaled <- scale(data.filtered, center = TRUE, scale = TRUE)
